            "id": 6007978,
            "title": "〈焦點股〉緯創5月營收暴衝2000億關卡 價量齊揚完成填息",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>) 受惠 AI 伺服器動能強勁，5 月營收達 2084.06 億元，首度站上 2000 億關卡，寫下單月歷史新高紀錄，激勵緯創今 (5) 日股價表現亮眼，價量齊揚，並完成填息。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007978%2Fl%2F5daba9f23862396d1dc661abeecdaeae.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">緯創5月營收暴衝2000億關卡，價量齊揚完成填息。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>緯創早盤以 120 元開高，最高漲至 120.5 元，漲逾半根停板，不過隨後漲幅收斂，截至 11 點 10 分，股價暫報 116.5 元，漲幅約 2.19%，站回 5 日線，成交爆量超過 5 萬張。此外，緯創周二 (3 日) 除息 3.8 元，在今日股價走揚下完成填息。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>至於三大法人近日籌碼動向，上周三大法人連續 4 個交易日買超，合計買超 4.4 萬張。不過於本周一 (2 日)、周二轉為賣方，昨天再回頭買超，本周一至周三合計賣超 2.1 萬張。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>緯創 5 月營收 2084.06 億元，月增 55.87%，年增 1.62 倍，寫下歷史單月新高；累計今年前 5 月營收 6885.94 億元，年增 76.39%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>緯創預期，第二季 PC 相關的三大產品季對季將有雙位數成長，AI 伺服器維持季對季三位數成長的表現，且將逐月往上。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
